# README: .env for Personal Website
# - This file stores environment variables for local development.
# - Do NOT commit secrets to version control. Add /.env to .gitignore.
# - Restart dev server after editing env values.
# - For framework-specific behavior, prefer .env.local (Next.js) or consult docs.

# Example variables (replace values; remove '#' to enable)
# SITE_TITLE="My Personal Website"
# NEXT_PUBLIC_API_BASE_URL="http://localhost:3000/api"
# DATABASE_URL="postgres://user:password@localhost:5432/dbname"
# SECRET_KEY="replace_with_strong_random_value"
# ANALYTICS_ID="UA-XXXXXXXXX-X"